sentences: She has curated Theremin100, a compilation featuring 50 international Theremin Artists to commemorate the Centennial of the Theremin in 2020.
She has performed and recorded as a solo artist since 2000.
In 2005, Chrysler and Suzanne Fiol co-founded the New York Theremin Society.
